<div
  class="mb-12 r_border-b-light bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-200 to-zinc-50 md:mb-32"
>
  <Navbar />
  <PageHeader
    @title="Data Sharing and Data Portals"
    @text="Your Data, Discoverable and Actionable."
  />
</div>

{{! Hero Section }}
<section class="container mb-16">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900 mb-4">We design and support data portals that fit your needs</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-700 mb-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      From entry-level data sharing through metadata catalogues, full-featured open data platforms, to resource-level portals where every dataset becomes a first-class citizen.
    </p>
    <LinkTo
      @route="contact"
      class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 rounded bg-red-700 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow shadow-red-500/10 hover:border-transparent hover:bg-red-600"
    >
      <span>Talk to us about your data portal</span>
      {{svg-jar "arrow-right" class="h-4"}}
    </LinkTo>
  </div>
</section>

{{! Why Work With Us Section }}
<section class="container mb-16">
  <div class="bg-zinc-100 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12">
    <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900">Why Work With Us</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed">
      At Redpencil, we know the common frustrations with data portals: they're hard to use, hard to maintain, and too often feel like dumping grounds instead of living tools. We solve this by focusing on usability, interoperability, and long-term sustainability. With experience in CKAN, our own <a href="https://data.gift"  rel="noopener" class="text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-500">>data.gift</a>, and custom semantic solutions, we'll help you set up or maintain a portal that truly works for your organization.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{{! Four Levels of Data Sharing Section }}
<section class="container mb-16">
  <h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-medium text-zinc-900 text-center">Four Levels of Data Sharing</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/distributed-small.svg"
      @title="Level 0: Entry-level data sharing"
      @text="Skip the complexity, start sharing today. We'll connect your data directly to major European portals (data.europa.eu, data.gov.be, datavindplaats.vlaanderen) through a simple endpoint—no portal maintenance required. You get instant visibility across multiple platforms while we handle DCAT compliance behind the scenes. Perfect for: First-time data publishers, resource-constrained teams, or organizations wanting maximum impact with minimal technical overhead."
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/data-modeling.svg"
      @title="Level 1: Metadata-only portals"
      @text="Your data catalog without the data headaches. Create a professional storefront that showcases all your datasets while keeping them exactly where they are. Users discover what you offer, you avoid duplicate storage costs and sync nightmares. It's the smart way to offer users a neat interface without reorganizing everything. Ideal for: Multi-department organizations, companies with legacy systems, or anyone needing quick wins without major infrastructure changes."
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/open-data.svg"
      @title="Level 2: Dataset-based portals"
      @text="The complete data sharing solution that works as hard as you do. Host, manage, and deliver your datasets through one branded platform with built-in APIs, user management, and automated workflows. We'll recommend the best technology stack for your specific needs—whether that's extending proven platforms or building custom solutions. Built for: Government agencies, established NGOs, and enterprises that need professional data publishing with full control and compliance features."
    />

    <ServiceCard
      @illustration="/assets/vector/linked-data.svg"
      @title="Level 3: Resource-based portals"
      @text="Future-proof your data strategy with intelligent connections. Every file, service, and data point gets its own web address and can link to related information automatically—transforming isolated datasets into a connected knowledge network. Built on our proven data.gift platform using cutting-edge linked data technology. Perfect for: Innovation-focused organizations, data-intensive enterprises, or government bodies building integrated digital ecosystems that need to scale."
    />
  </div>
</section>

